false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44591, "create_time": 1646707968, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Francis: 好的，谢谢francis！", "timestamp": 1646707968}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44594, "create_time": 1646708152, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Francis: 我听说是新源县有很多封闭式教培中心，而且有当地人控诉管理的警察动用暴力和强制绝育", "timestamp": 1646708152}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44597, "create_time": 1646708591, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "希望大家还是有时间真正去新疆走一走，自己眼睛看到的比听到的要有说服力很多，看过生活过再做评判", "timestamp": 1646708591}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44599, "create_time": 1646709212, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Francis: 还有五家渠市", "timestamp": 1646709212}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44600, "create_time": 1646709228, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Francis: 不知道francis是否熟悉这两个地方", "timestamp": 1646709228}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44606, "create_time": 1646709492, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "另外大家身边民族同学可能还是比较少，建议多问问他们的自身感受，比其他报道的导向性可能要少，更真实一些", "timestamp": 1646709492}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44610, "create_time": 1646709817, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "新源在巩乃斯林场附近，是比较著名的景点了，五家渠去过一次，了解不多。但是从小在新疆长大，还真没听说过类似“集中营”的教培中心一类的东西。民族的同化在哪里都不可避免，但是这种极端的手段如果有的话，我相信怎么都压不下去，早就爆出来了", "timestamp": 1646709817}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44611, "create_time": 1646709872, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Francis: 可是巴州离内地比较近，被报告出现集中管理和绝育的地方基本上都在新疆西北部，而这些地方普通人去会有生命安全，轻易也不会让你过去看", "timestamp": 1646709872}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44613, "create_time": 1646710006, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 9, "text": "Re 洞主: 差不多得了，不教维语就是文化灭绝？属实是有点自我意识过剩了。所有的多民族国家是不是所有语种都得教啊", "timestamp": 1646710006}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44614, "create_time": 1646710007, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Francis: 以及集中管控和教培中心都是近五年出现的（第一次报告被强制带入教培中心出现在2017年四月，一直持续至今）", "timestamp": 1646710007}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44615, "create_time": 1646710036, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Isabella: 我汉族人😅谁自我意识过剩了", "timestamp": 1646710036}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44616, "create_time": 1646710166, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Francis: francis是不是17年左右已经入学了，以及第一批得以离开教培中心的人是在大概九个月后，也就是在18年之后，还有至今没有离开教培中心的", "timestamp": 1646710166}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44623, "create_time": 1646710389, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 10, "text": "集中管控不知道，教培中心确实是有的。我妈是小学老师，以前去新疆出差过一段时间…", "timestamp": 1646710389}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44624, "create_time": 1646710402, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re 洞主: 建议dz如果真的对这个问题感兴趣，还是多去新疆走走，就当旅游也不亏。至于新疆的治安，去了实际体会一下就知道了。西北部离国境线比较近，一些势力很容易渗透，关于那里的宣传，要注意明辨。总之，花时间去调研比在网上看消息要清楚的多", "timestamp": 1646710402}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44625, "create_time": 1646710652, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Francis: 确实。我身边汉族同学只有体制内的才敢去伊犁这样的地区，并且通常有当地政府派人陪同。dz很想去但还是有些担心", "timestamp": 1646710652}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44626, "create_time": 1646710657, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re 洞主: 想知道dz是在哪里看到的强制教培😂，因为我也只是没有听说，不能保证一定没有或者是宣传问题，想看一看来源", "timestamp": 1646710657}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44627, "create_time": 1646710732, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Jason: 是封闭式的教培中心吗？还是就是普通的", "timestamp": 1646710732}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44630, "create_time": 1646710814, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re 洞主: 之前和家里人也去过喀什、伊犁、霍尔果斯之类靠近边境的地方，还真没有什么政府派人（可能是地位太低了？），安安全全没什么害怕的呀😂", "timestamp": 1646710814}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44631, "create_time": 1646710829, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Francis: 我看前面几个cz说的教培中心😂为了表达得缓和一些所以这么说。我听说的只有集中营和绝育", "timestamp": 1646710829}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44633, "create_time": 1646710891, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Francis: 太奇怪了，那些家里体制内的同学都是由当地警察陪同才敢参观的（尤其是北疆", "timestamp": 1646710891}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44634, "create_time": 1646710933, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re 洞主: 可能外地游客确实会因为一些原因更担心自身安全一点吧，但是本地人真的不怕", "timestamp": 1646710933}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44637, "create_time": 1646711126, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re 洞主: 我说的直一些，警察哪有那么多时间去陪着参观啊，当然如果他等级高需要特殊保护那另说，一般人还真没见出动警力陪同参观的。另外想看看dz消息的来源，了解一下", "timestamp": 1646711126}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44638, "create_time": 1646711167, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Francis: 有道理", "timestamp": 1646711167}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44639, "create_time": 1646711187, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 10, "text": "Re 洞主: 我不清楚具体情况，但是我听到的一个细节还挺吓人的 派过去的老师给当地的老师培训的时候，双方是隔着铁栏杆的…而且培训前会先花差不多半个小时的时间点名 这是好几年前的事了，不知道现在还会不会这样", "timestamp": 1646711187}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44642, "create_time": 1646711363, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Jason: 有没有一种可能，你说的是他们在给监狱里的犯人普及文化知识，而不是教师培训😂", "timestamp": 1646711363}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44643, "create_time": 1646711450, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 10, "text": "Re Jason: 不过除此之外也好像没什么特别的地方 （反正我妈玩的挺开心的…跟公费旅游差不多）", "timestamp": 1646711450}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44644, "create_time": 1646711486, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Francis: https://xinjiang.sppga.ubc.ca/critical-scholarship/academic-publications/bulldozing-culture-chinas-systematic-destruction-of-uyghur-heritage-reveals-genocidal-intent/", "timestamp": 1646711486}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44646, "create_time": 1646711549, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "我们学校也有北师大的老师来培训，下面团场和偏远地区的学校也有教师培训的，但这种情形（铁栅栏）还真没听说，也不太可能，他们难道是野兽吗需要关起来？也不会抗议？那怎么教育学生啊", "timestamp": 1646711549}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44647, "create_time": 1646711554, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 10, "text": "Re Francis: 不不 他们是作为老师去对口支援的，这个可以肯定 我妈也就是小学行政领导的级别而已", "timestamp": 1646711554}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44652, "create_time": 1646711618, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Jason: 哇…这个确实好奇怪", "timestamp": 1646711618}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44661, "create_time": 1646711897, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 10, "text": "Re 洞主: 可能是为了避免冲突吧 我印象里那时候新疆地区是有点紧张的，普通人会不太敢去 安检查的很严，会要求你脱鞋 当时还听我妈讲新疆课本之类的闹jiangdu的问题来着的", "timestamp": 1646711897}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44663, "create_time": 1646711949, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Jason: 那是哪一年呀？", "timestamp": 1646711949}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44664, "create_time": 1646711998, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re 洞主: 为了城市建设拆除过于老旧且历史意义不大的清真寺和为了文化灭绝而破坏都可以选择性报道成“推平”（只是举例），但事实是什么需要真正客观的视角和对整件事历史的熟悉，媒介素养在现在我觉得很难培养（不是说dz），毕竟导向性的报道如果不是真正了解很难去分辨。这件事我再了解了解，但我认为是不存在的，或者说有一定歪曲和主观因素在里面😂", "timestamp": 1646711998}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44666, "create_time": 1646712159, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Jason: 这个问题（安检，课本）确实有过，不过涉及的方面比较多，三言两语不太能简单讲清。建议大家可以看看《暗流涌动》这部纪录片，可能会对新疆的局势和历史多一点点了解", "timestamp": 1646712159}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44667, "create_time": 1646712255, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 10, "text": "Re 洞主: 六七年前的样子吧 我感觉现在没有就没有这种情绪了", "timestamp": 1646712255}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44669, "create_time": 1646712283, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Francis: 好的好的，我理解francis的观点，因为我去年也是这样想，现在有些怀疑了。可能是国内各种矫枉过正的清零政策和信息封锁让我觉得以gcd的尿性干的出来集中营和群体绝育这种事。francis了解完之后打算发在哪里？dz到时候可以继续讨论", "timestamp": 1646712283}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44671, "create_time": 1646712542, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Francis: 而且听我爸妈说当年计划生育在农村实行的时候基本上就是强制绝育+集中劳动", "timestamp": 1646712542}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44673, "create_time": 1646712563, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Jason: 好的，谢谢jason～", "timestamp": 1646712563}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44683, "create_time": 1646712863, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 11, "text": "[tmp]\nhttps://2047.one/t/17641", "timestamp": 1646712863}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44685, "create_time": 1646712980, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Kate: kate认为可信度如何", "timestamp": 1646712980}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44688, "create_time": 1646713036, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Kate: 说实话我很震惊，和我听到的证言时间线以及场景/具体事件都对上了", "timestamp": 1646713036}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44731, "create_time": 1646714598, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re 洞主: 我还没想好写在哪😂，想写在洞里但是感觉写长篇不太方便，其他地方的安全性不太放心...先在这个洞里零碎写一些吧，等后面整理一下单独开个洞", "timestamp": 1646714598}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44737, "create_time": 1646714717, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "我其实挺想好好研究一下这个问题的，一方面帮助大家了解新疆，一方面也让我自己更清楚的看看这个我生活了快二十年的地方", "timestamp": 1646714717}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44739, "create_time": 1646714810, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Francis: 好的～到时候建了新洞在这里放个洞号吧，我之后会回来看", "timestamp": 1646714810}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44741, "create_time": 1646714904, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Francis: 好！感谢francis", "timestamp": 1646714904}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44747, "create_time": 1646715273, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 10, "text": "Re 洞主: 刚刚去查了一下我妈的qq空间，准确时间是在2015年7月底8月初", "timestamp": 1646715273}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44750, "create_time": 1646715390, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 10, "text": "Re Jason: 所以确实是教师培训，避免他们给学生传播jiangdu思想", "timestamp": 1646715390}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44759, "create_time": 1646715599, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Jason: 好的，谢谢jason！", "timestamp": 1646715599}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44766, "create_time": 1646715744, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "#16671 感兴趣的dym可以关注一下，可能更新时间间隔比较长，希望大家耐心等待。如果有不同意的地方可以整理一下发出来，共同探讨。等后期会整理，另外发个整合后的", "timestamp": 1646715744}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44770, "create_time": 1646715826, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "这个洞里的问题也会简要回复一下我的了解，完整版还是请到新洞，感谢", "timestamp": 1646715826}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44852, "create_time": 1646717994, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "关于安检：新疆的安检历来（7·5事件之后？）是出了名的严格，当然与新疆独特的环境有很大关系。（为了防止可能发生的暴力恐怖事件，）乘坐火车会经过三道左右的安检程序（至于这三道有没有区别我也不太清楚，应该是有的）。而机场的安检更为严格，需要脱下鞋子，也会用金属探测仪检查脚底，身上会严格检查，包括手臂、前胸、后背、腰部、臀部（口袋）、腿部都会检查（这一点作为新疆人也会觉得不舒服，不过听说新的政委上任后会有改变）其他地方（路上的检查卡点）大量减少，以前需要刷身份证，现在大多不再检查", "timestamp": 1646717994}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44867, "create_time": 1646718424, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Francis: 不过其中还有一个备受关注和议论的问题就是对什么车辆进行检查。官方的解释是抽查，不过在实际执行中发现是否详细检查（刷身份证登记）似乎和民族有很大关系。如果司机和乘客都是汉族，很大概率会被直接放行，而如果是民族同胞大多会让刷身份证（限于出入主城区的小型检查站，大的检查站一视同仁），在这一点上我认为确实存在民族间的不平等，只是不知道是政府的本意还是基层的执行问题", "timestamp": 1646718424}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44874, "create_time": 1646718795, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Francis: 支持francis", "timestamp": 1646718795}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44877, "create_time": 1646719093, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "关于课本：在一些学校是开设双语班的，说白了就是有汉族同学为主（也会有民族同学）的汉语班，也有全部由民族同学组成的民族班。在几年前（2017左右，误差较大）曾经曝出民族班使用的民语课本（主要是维语课本，据说也有哈语课本）中存在宣传疆独的内容。原因可能是分裂势力进入了编写组（民语课本是地方编写的），而因为缺少民语翻译人才，对民语课本的审核并不严格，导致这一内容长期（可能存在了数年）无人发现，据说最后是一位民族学生家长发现并上报的。出事之后（教育局？）组织了对教材的审核，更换了原有教材，对相关人员进行了处理（处理责任人不太清楚，但教材是更换了）", "timestamp": 1646719093}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44886, "create_time": 1646719359, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "以上两点是我的个人观察（安检是切身体会，课本是从一位双语小学的老师那里了解的），个人认为可信度在80%左右，基本事实应该没有错误，具体细节可能会有出入。供大家参考", "timestamp": 1646719359}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44892, "create_time": 1646720376, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "https://www.newyorker.com/magazine/a-reporter-at-large/magazine/2021/04/12/surviving-the-crackdown-in-xinjiang-translation-mandarin-raffi-khatchadourian\n更一篇纽约客文章链接，可信度很高", "timestamp": 1646720376}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44896, "create_time": 1646720829, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 12, "text": "[tmp]\n蛮荒之地，无事生非", "timestamp": 1646720829}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44898, "create_time": 1646720891, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "悲，发现以一己之力想要理清事情的全貌困难真的不小，容我慢慢收集分析", "timestamp": 1646720891}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44901, "create_time": 1646720948, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 12, "text": "[tmp]\n东欧这么多民族问题，乌克兰问题车臣问题，亚美尼亚阿塞拜疆问题，就是因为斯大林“种族灭绝”做少了", "timestamp": 1646720948}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44907, "create_time": 1646721198, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Louis: 什么逻辑，你咋不说这么多问题就是因为人类这种生物还没灭绝", "timestamp": 1646721198}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44908, "create_time": 1646721242, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Francis: 还挺像做毕设的😂", "timestamp": 1646721242}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44909, "create_time": 1646721263, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 13, "text": "[tmp]\n亚洲的民族问题本来比美国人种问题简单多了。都是黄种人只要通婚移民管控就行了，哪有什么尖锐不可调和矛盾。上代人固守的民族传统不必带到新一代的年轻人", "timestamp": 1646721263}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44911, "create_time": 1646721428, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 13, "text": "[tmp]\n我看到的小学生课本里分裂激进主义内容真是欠图", "timestamp": 1646721428}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44913, "create_time": 1646721548, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 13, "text": "[tmp]\n激进民族主义就像本拉登一样，萨达姆称本拉登为神经病疯子", "timestamp": 1646721548}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44925, "create_time": 1646722079, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "我还是希望能够不带zz立场的去看待这个问题，一旦带入了立场，对于很多判断会有错位", "timestamp": 1646722079}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44937, "create_time": 1646722812, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Francis: 确实", "timestamp": 1646722812}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44941, "create_time": 1646722923, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "就我而言，并不是要替政府（或者某zz团体、党派）洗地，我真的只希望我的家乡能够展现他本来的样子，希望大家能够正视这一方水土和生活在这里的人们。但是说实话我现在有一点害怕，因为中立的观点很容易被反对的人看作是在支持另一方。我相信这里的匿名性，所以我想不受限制的说出我亲身的观察，但匿名降低了对自己观点需要负的责任（不是zz责任，而是坚持并能够讲出自己观点道理的责任）。还是那句话，想要真正理解这个问题，必须暂时放下自己固有的立场，放弃“选择性相信”。当然，我的观点同样不能保证完全的客观公正，唯一的办法还是去实际调研，或者足够深入的亲身体会。", "timestamp": 1646722923}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44944, "create_time": 1646723002, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 14, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Margaret: 这下回纥人成小黄人了", "timestamp": 1646723002}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44945, "create_time": 1646723034, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 15, "text": "Re 洞主: 洞主的问题不就是问的政治吗。民族融合是一劳永逸的短暂阵痛", "timestamp": 1646723034}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 44961, "create_time": 1646724360, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Francis: 可能我刚才没有表达清楚，也许这个问题最后是为了zz立场服务的，但我觉得合适的方式是通过结论来佐证或者调整立场，而不是通过立场来得出结论。客观公正的结论永远应该是忠于事实的，而不是忠于立场的。", "timestamp": 1646724360}], "create_time": 1646699591, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1646724360, "likenum": 19, "n_attentions": 19, "n_comments": 94, "pid": 16614, "poll": null, "reply": 94, "text": "dym如何看待新疆问题？集中营和强制绝育确实非人道，为何gcd要搞这种事？", "timestamp": 1646699591}}